üéì Startathon AI: Facilitator & League Toolkit
Empowering the Next Generation of AI-First Founders
Welcome to the Startathon AI League implementation guide. This toolkit is designed to help academic leaders, department chairs, and student organizers launch a high-impact AI entrepreneurship competition at their institution with minimal overhead.
üìå Overview
Startathon AI is not just a hackathon; it is a validated pedagogical framework that teaches students to use Large Language Models (LLMs) as co-founders. By participating in the Maryland Community College AI League (MCCAIL), your institution joins a statewide network focused on "Series A Readiness" and workforce innovation.
